cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NA. 

The paper deals with image processing and machine learning techniques applied to ultrasound imaging, which suggests a primary category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of deep learning and iterative algorithms also suggests a secondary category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves signal processing and optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). Finally, the use of simulations and in-vivo experiments suggests a possible category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
